</code></pre><h2 id='list-allergy-sub-resources'>List allergy sub resources</h2>
<ul>
<li><p>List allergy sub resource by it&#39;s UUID and parent patient UUID.</p>

<p>Retrieve a <b>allergy</b> sub resources of a <b>patient</b> resource. Returns a <code>404 Not Found</code> status if allergy not exists. If you are not logged in to perform this action, a <code>401 Unauthorized</code> status returned. </p></li>
</ul>
